---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Dresurno jahanje" activePage="/konjicki-sport">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-content">
      <div class="page-hero-breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Naslovnica</a>
        <span class="sep">›</span>
        <a href="/konjicki-sport">Konjički sport</a>
        <span class="sep">›</span>
        <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">Dresurno jahanje</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Dresurno jahanje</h1>
      <p>Temeljna disciplina konjičkog sporta — elegancija, sklad i savršena harmonija jahača i konja.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="discipline-block reverse reveal">
      <div class="discipline-img">
        <img src="/images/dresurno.jpg" alt="Dresurno jahanje">
        <span class="discipline-img-badge">Temeljna disciplina</span>
      </div>
      <div class="discipline-text">
        <div class="discipline-number">02</div>
        <h2>Dresurno jahanje</h2>
        <p>Dresurno jahanje svakako je temeljna disciplina konjičkog sporta u kojoj se isprepliće sport i umjetnost suradnje jahača i konja — s ciljem da se izvedu testovi koji u sebi sadrže razne načine kretanja konja i prelazaka iz hoda u kas pa natrag u hod, te zaustavljanja na unaprijed određenim pozicijama, sve to uz poštivanje obrazaca kretnji i figura.</p>
        <p>Jahač i konj u suradnji izvode unaprijed definirane testove koje moraju znati napamet i bez pomoći sa strane. Iznimku od ovoga čine "Freestyle" testovi u kojima sam jahač definira vlastitu koreografiju koju izvodi uz glazbu.</p>
        <p>U posljednjih par godina dresurno jahanje privlači sve veći broj mladih natjecatelja, među kojima brojnošću i kvalitetom dominiraju žene.</p>
        <div class="discipline-features">
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Elegancija</span>
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Sklad</span>
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Tehnička izvedba</span>
          <span class="discipline-feature"><svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Freestyle uz glazbu</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="rules-section section">
    <div class="rules-inner reveal">
      <h2>Klubovi dresurnog jahanja u ZKS-u</h2>
      <p>U okviru Zagrebačkog konjičkog saveza dresurnim sportom se bave:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Konjički klub Breza</li>
        <li>Purgerski konjički klub</li>
        <li>Konjički klub Jarun</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="nav-disciplines section">
    <div class="nav-disciplines-inner reveal">
      <h3>Ostale discipline</h3>
      <div class="other-disciplines">
        <a href="/preponsko-jahanje" class="other-card">
          <div class="other-card-bg" style="background-image:url('/images/preponsko.jpg')"></div>
          <div class="other-card-overlay"></div>
          <span>Preponsko jahanje</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/daljinsko-jahanje" class="other-card">
          <div class="other-card-bg" style="background-image:url('/images/daljinsko.jpg')"></div>
          <div class="other-card-overlay"></div>
          <span>Daljinsko jahanje</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .discipline-block { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .discipline-block.reverse { direction: rtl; }
  .discipline-block.reverse > * { direction: ltr; }
  .discipline-img { border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 4/3; position: relative; }
  .discipline-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .discipline-img-badge { position: absolute; top: 1rem; left: 1rem; background: var(--blue); color: #fff; padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .discipline-block.reverse .discipline-img-badge { left: auto; right: 1rem; }
  .discipline-number { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue-pale); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .discipline-text h2 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-800); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .discipline-text p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
  .discipline-features { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .discipline-feature { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.35rem; background: var(--blue-pale); color: var(--blue); padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .discipline-feature svg { width: 12px; height: 12px; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .rules-section { background: var(--off-white); }
  .rules-inner { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .rules-inner h2 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-800); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .rules-inner p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .rules-inner ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; color: var(--gray-600); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 2; }

  .nav-disciplines { background: var(--white); }
  .nav-disciplines-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .nav-disciplines-inner h3 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-800); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .other-disciplines { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .other-card { position: relative; border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 16/7; text-decoration: none; display: block; }
  .other-card-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; background-size: cover; background-position: center; transition: transform 0.5s; }
  .other-card:hover .other-card-bg { transform: scale(1.05); }
  .other-card-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(27,58,107,0.85) 0%, rgba(27,58,107,0.3) 100%); }
  .other-card span { position: absolute; bottom: 1.2rem; left: 1.5rem; color: #fff; font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .discipline-block, .discipline-block.reverse { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; direction: ltr; }
    .other-disciplines { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
